Title : Kondopoga Bay
Text : [[File:Brockhaus and Efron Encyclopedic Dictionary b42 946-0.jpg|A depth map of the Onego Lake|thumb|right|200px]]
The '''Kondopoga Bay''' ({{lang-ru|Кондопожская губа}}, '''Kondopozhskaya Bay''') is a bay (length 32&nbsp;km, width over 8&nbsp;km, max depth 78m) in the northwestern part of the  [[Karelia]]n part of the [[Onega Lake]], [[Russia]] .<ref name=efron>{{efron|wstitle=Кондопожская губа}}</ref>

